    {
      "q": "What is premium logo placement?",
      "a": "Preferential treatment on all logo benefits (first, centered, larger), plus your logo on attendee badges and lanyards."
    },
    {
      "q": "What is top billing?",
      "a": "Diamond sponsors are always listed first and acknowledged as “Special Thanks to our Diamond Sponsors”."
    },
    {
      "q": "How does the attendee list work?",
      "a": "A CSV (name, email, job title, company) of attendees who opt in at registration. Gold and Diamond only."
    },
    {
      "q": "How does the job board work?",
      "a": "Your listings appear on the event website and go out by email to all attendees. Open to every sponsor tier, up to 5 roles each."
    },
    {
      "q": "Who invoices us, and in what currency?",
      "a": "OSSFE 2027 is organised with the MIT Plasma Science and Fusion Center, which handles the finances and legal side. MIT invoices in USD and payment is by wire transfer, with no deduction for taxes or fees."
